{"FOAL":[{"def":"The young of any animal of the Horse family (Equidæ); a colt; a filly.","pos":""}],"FOAM":[{"def":"The white substance, consisting of an aggregation of bubbles, which is formed on the surface of liquids,or in the mouth of an animal, by violent agitation or fermentation; froth; spume; scum; as, the foam of the sea.","pos":""}],"FOAMINGLY":[{"def":"With foam; frothily.","pos":""}],"FOAMY":[{"def":"Covered with foam; frothy; spumy.","pos":""}]}